# HealthCare Billing Analysis

A Healthcare Billing Analytics and Fraud Detection system built using Python, Machine Learning, and Streamlit.  
This project analyzes healthcare billing data, predicts billing patterns, and provides insights through an interactive dashboard.

---

## Features

- Healthcare billing prediction
- Fraud/anomaly detection analysis
- Interactive Streamlit dashboard
- Data preprocessing and visualization
- Machine learning model integration
- Analytics and reporting
- Real-time prediction interface

---

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Streamlit
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Machine Learning
- Data Analytics

---

## Project Structure

```bash
HealthCare-Billing-Analysis/
│
├── app.py
├── model.py
├── spark_analysis.py
├── README.md
├── screenshots/
│   ├── dashboard.png
│   ├── prediction.png
│   └── analytics.png
│
├── data/
│   ├── final_healthcare_billing.csv
│   └── requirements.txt
```

---

## Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Sruthi0704/HealthCare-Billing-Analysis.git
```

Move into the project directory:

```bash
cd HealthCare-Billing-Analysis
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
pip install -r data/requirements.txt
```

---

## Running the Project

Start the Streamlit application:

```bash
streamlit run app.py
```

Open in browser:

```bash
http://localhost:8501
```

